dc_description_s: This line data layer represents roads for Calumet County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Calumet_Roads_2018.gdb. [This data represents the centerlines of all roads in Calumet County. The data is used in nearly all aspects of the Land Information Office and is updated almost every day. Updates are performed using source documents (surveys, plats, etc) along with any available aerial imagery.]
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
